573
00:33:01,888 --> 00:33:03,320
But I don't have a boyfriend.

574
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:04,280
You...

575
00:33:06,466 --> 00:33:07,600
I'll return to work first.

576
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:08,600
Come here.

577
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:22,360
After two days of serious training,

578
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,844
I'm now familiar with the basics

579
00:33:23,888 --> 00:33:25,600
of housekeeping and work procedures.

580
00:33:25,888 --> 00:33:27,222
I can give it a five-star review.

581
00:33:27,222 --> 00:33:28,990
Is this what you mean
by a five-star review?

582
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:33,680
Come with me.

583
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:41,360
The toothbrush labels
are placed differently.

584
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:46,400
The labels have not been
aligned to the same level.

585
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:50,440
The soap box isn't centered.

586
00:33:51,520 --> 00:33:54,440
There are water stains
and marks all over the basin.

587
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:58,600
There are fingerprints on the tap.

588
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,000
Negative review.

589
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,977
(Negative Review)

590
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,440
There's hair on the floor

591
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:13,920
and dust in the air.

592
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:19,120
Boss, that's your hair.

593
00:34:31,577 --> 00:34:33,000
You didn't clean the refrigerator.

594
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:34,160
Negative review.

595
00:34:35,680 --> 00:34:36,960
I did forget about that.

596
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,080
I was nervous because you were here.

597
00:34:40,422 --> 00:34:41,560
I acknowledge your effort.

598
00:34:41,570 --> 00:34:42,500
But you saw the result.

599
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:43,350
I can only give you...

600
00:34:43,355 --> 00:34:44,160
A negative review.

601
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,440
I know that.

602
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,240
But aren't you being too strict

603
00:34:47,266 --> 00:34:48,777
for judging the efforts of an intern

604
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:50,240
with such high standards?

605
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:52,760
Everyone has the right to question.

606
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,639
In Spring Sea,
everything has to be perfect.

607
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,720
We can't just make do with everything,
like your English.

608
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:57,560
Yes, sir.

609
00:34:57,800 --> 00:35:00,560
There's no perfect service in the world.

610
00:35:01,555 --> 00:35:03,920
In that case, you should
start with the turndown service.

611
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,720
Wait. Why is there a new task?

612
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,880
What service?

613
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,320
Turndown service.

614
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:11,760
I'll inspect your work tonight.

615
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:19,040
Turndown service?

616
00:35:37,777 --> 00:35:39,111
Is there something on your mind?

617
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,120
Nothing.

618
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,680
I just want to ask you

619
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:49,760
if our hotel provides
any special services

620
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,880
to our guests at night?

621
00:35:57,080 --> 00:35:58,840
You mean turndown service?

622
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:01,480
Lower your volume.

623
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,440
That's normal.

624
00:36:04,466 --> 00:36:06,066
Even if no guests request us to do so,

625
00:36:06,111 --> 00:36:07,720
we should do it every day.

626
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,120
It's normal?

627
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,840
We should do them every day?

628
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,480
We start from 8 P.M.

629
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,760
It usually ends at 8:30 P.M.

630
00:36:15,911 --> 00:36:17,560
Who are you providing the service to?

631
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:19,160
Have you reached that stage already?

632
00:36:19,866 --> 00:36:21,222
What were you two chatting about?

633
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:26,080
Let me ask you something.

634
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:29,760
Have you done a turndown service before?

635
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:30,800
Yeah.

636
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,400
You too?

637
00:36:32,533 --> 00:36:34,311
Did the God of Plague
force you to do so?

638
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:37,200
I don't think so.

639
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:38,720
It's all part of work.

640
00:36:52,080 --> 00:36:53,840
It's only been a few days.

641
00:36:54,555 --> 00:36:57,400
I can't believe I have to go through
the industry's unspoken rules.

642
00:36:57,888 --> 00:36:59,400
How dare he mention it in front of me?

643
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,800
Do I look like that sort of person?

644
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:03,720
I don't think he's someone like that.

645
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,880
I think you should clarify it first.

646
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:07,480
It might be a misunderstanding.

647
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:09,880
I've already inquired about it.

648
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,040
Everyone was already used to it.

649
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,560
He's so despicable.

650
00:37:15,040 --> 00:37:16,080
What an animal.

651
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:19,160
I can't believe that your hotel
would do such a thing.

652
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,280
What do you plan to do, then?

653
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,680
I need to expose them.

654
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,720
Later, I'll use
the procedure to my advantage.

655
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:29,880
I'll record the entire process

656
00:37:30,111 --> 00:37:31,480
and post it for the world to see.

657
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:34,080
Stop. It's too risky for you
to head there alone.

658
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,320
I have to join you.

659
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:36,600
Don't worry.

660
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,880
I'll be super cautious.

661
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,760
