665
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,880
Or should I prepare some tools?

666
00:37:53,155 --> 00:37:53,840
Stop right there.

667
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,400
Why do I feel like

668
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:58,000
