669
00:38:00,022 --> 00:38:01,222
Don't spout nonsense.

670
00:38:01,666 --> 00:38:02,440
That's not true.

671
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:03,880
Stop lying.

672
00:38:04,311 --> 00:38:04,960
That's not true.

673
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,040
You're still denying it?

674
00:39:09,288 --> 00:39:11,800
I can't catch the bad guys
without sacrificing myself.

675
00:39:11,933 --> 00:39:13,733
I have to enter
the lion's den this time.

676
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,680
Come in. I'm ready.

677
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,960
You're finally here.

678
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:23,160
Come in.

679
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:33,440
What are you doing?

680
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:40,120
Didn't you request a turndown service?

681
00:40:40,266 --> 00:40:41,800
I don't like it when the lights are on.

682
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,440
What are you doing, then?

683
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,120
I'm ready. Let's get started.

684
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:47,360
